Experience of establishing and running at least 05 Computer labs-based ICT projects with minimum 100 nodes with exposure of running ICT labs with value of about 70 to 100 Crores for a period of minimum 07 years. 
The Bidder should have undertaken at least 03 similar nature of projects (Running ICT Labs on Leased Space) across the country with the value not less than INR 02 Crores each. Similar nature projects constitute setting up of computer lab which includes Computer H/W, Network, Electrification, Furniture, Surveillance and Manpower to maintain and operate etc.
This shall cover the details of works of similar nature, approximate magnitude and duration carried out for last 03 years and / or current work along with a certificate from the organisation where the job was carried out. Work completion certificate / experience certificate of having successfully completed at least three (03) work of similar magnitude must be submitted with Particulars of Experience (attach certificates, testimonials) along with Self-attested photo copy should be enclosed

Bidder are requested to refer SECTION VII - Request for clarification of bid document against Pre-Bid Query. Pre-Bid Query Format is attached for your ready reference. 
All Pre-bid Query must reach at least 02 days before scheduled Pre-Bid Query. Pre-bid query received after the schedule date shall not be entertained
